{"tid":769821,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"反派「靶眼」與「夜魔俠」一同鍛鍊！《漫威夜魔俠》第三季確定2018年上線","createTime":"2018-08-06T13:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T14:49:10.000Z","uid":49391,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"15328f01ff96e74adbb88a1d7f373f38c18d56ae","tid":769821,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.dramaqueen.com.tw/images/news/20180806161323530249be1b2bbdd3994a6ae25a593d785a86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dramaqueen.com.tw%2Fimages%2Fnews%2F20180806161323530249be1b2bbdd3994a6ae25a593d785a86.jpg&h=cf6fddde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNetflix 漫威美劇《漫威夜魔俠》（Marvel's Daredevil）第三季將讓反派角色「靶眼」（Bullseye）登場的傳聞不斷。繼幕後工作人員上傳工作服露餡後，健身機構 Arazi 私人教練日前的 PO 文則證實該角色的確將現身，並由《南國醫戀》（Hart Of Dixie）男星威爾森貝塞爾（Wilson Bethel）飾演。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n從該張照片中可看到主演查理考克斯（Charlie Cox）、威爾森貝塞爾在辛苦訓練後，大汗淋漓的模樣。該教練也同時在 PO 文中標記 #夜魔俠 和 #靶眼 ，說道：「第三季的《漫威夜魔俠》將會非常瘋狂！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://instagram.com/p/BmCGTrrhVqQ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=embed_loading_state_control\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBmCGTrrhVqQ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dembed_loading_state_control&h=8cba0b3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此外，由於 Netflix 漫威系列美劇已有三部排定在今年回歸，包括《漫威潔西卡瓊斯》（Marvel's Jessica Jones）、《漫威盧克凱奇》（Marvel's Luke Cage）以及將於 9 月 7 日上線第二季的《漫威鐵拳俠》（Marvel's Iron Fist），因此讓人揣測《《漫威夜魔俠》第三季有可能會在 2019 年才推出。不過該線上影音平台的執行長泰德薩蘭多斯（Ted Sarandos）先前在 Q2 收益訪談的影片中，提到下半年將回歸的劇集，當中就有《漫威夜魔俠》，證實粉絲可在今年就看到第三季。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n第三季除了威爾森貝塞爾外，其餘加盟演員包括《如此一家人》（The Fosters）男星傑阿里（Jay Ali）、《花邊教主》（Gossip Girl）女星瓊安華莉（Joanne Whalley）。首兩季反派「金霸王」文森唐諾佛利歐（Vincent D Onofrio）也確定回歸。"},{"pid":"74e46c8ed15a46bac522dcd2731d4c3a5f0eeeba","tid":769821,"uid":10657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:21:28.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"503c14e8bbb5411b7b1be8459d5cd95d5effd968","tid":769821,"uid":133533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:21:52.000Z","msg":"髮線失守"},{"pid":"a91762c420d7ab8f4fd0ea5326b4cb5e4d85133e","tid":769821,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:29:56.000Z","msg":"之前睇左罰叔<br />\n遲d煲返夜魔俠,有d集數有罰叔出場"},{"pid":"449320d4576f0d39c3b2215d94ab9179c3a68758","tid":769821,"uid":35112,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:35:34.000Z","msg":"條友影相都好似真係盲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19cb8021a176f058668e13e910bac818e5ce00d","tid":769821,"uid":48222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:38:39.000Z","msg":"應該11月"},{"pid":"945f352fc2a13b4d746e16d608d6f58e8e8857dd","tid":769821,"uid":24524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"449320d4576f0d39c3b2215d94ab9179c3a68758","tid":769821,"uid":35112,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:35:34.000Z","msg":"條友影相都好似真係盲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:41:13.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff7754c28d26812ea96897ede14449464e7fab1","tid":769821,"uid":24524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a748a9ff7f6b18cfabbd395e100dfbfe7939c7","tid":769821,"uid":2545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:41:51.000Z","msg":"不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj